    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>True Definition of Husband</strong>&mdash;The home is an institution of God. God designed that the family circle, father, mother, and children, should exist in this world as a firm.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">1<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 36, 1899\" data-link=\"14064.4750001\">Manuscript 36, 1899</span>.</span></a></sup>",
