    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "His name, &ldquo;house-band,&rdquo; is the true definition of husband.... I saw that but few fathers realize their responsibility.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">3<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"1T 547.1\" data-link=\"116.2535\">Testimonies for the Church 1:547</span>.</span></a></sup>",
