    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "The father should do his part toward making home happy. Whatever his cares and business perplexities, they should not be permitted to overshadow his family; <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"212\"></span> he should enter his home with smiles and pleasant words.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">4<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"MH 390.1\" data-link=\"135.1971\">The Ministry of Healing, 390, 392</span>.</span></a></sup>",
