    "refcode_long": "The Adventist Home, p. 212.3 (Ellen Gould White)",
    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "The father must not betray his sacred trust. He must not, on any point, yield up his parental authority.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">7<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Lt 9, 1904\" data-link=\"14069.8334001\">Letter 9, 1904</span>.</span></a></sup>",
