    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Maturity of Experience Called For</strong>&mdash;A father must not be as a child, moved merely by impulse. He is bound to his family by sacred, holy ties.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">9<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"1T 547.1\" data-link=\"116.2535\">Testimonies for the Church 1:547</span>.</span></a></sup>",
